node.text:
I’ve included in this video bird of paradise with wall support, as well as standing compass.
I love using the wall as a tool to access a deeper understanding of standing poses, and then applying that new information while standing in my balancing pose. When you use the wall, still keep an awareness on the standing leg - grounding evenly into the foot, contracting the thigh and maintaining stability.
At the end of the video is how I used to use the strap when I was first learning the shoulder rotation!
#yoga #wallstuff
Wearing @aloyoga cargo leggings in bone #sponsored
Song by @danakosber

I’m releasing my own app!
🌼💛
this has been months of work and filming all over- and I’m so excited to finally share it with you. it’s releasing in just a few weeks.
the app will have classes ranging from 5-10 minutes up to 60+ minutes, from beginner to advanced, and it will have yoga, Pilates, barre and meditation!
I’ve filmed in some of my favourite locations ever and I can’t wait to practice together from all around the 🌏

if you’re subscribed to my newsletter, you get early access to the app, special discounts + access to free live seasonal community classes. click the link in my bio- sooo excited to have you with me in this new chapter!

first free community class:
flexibility fundamentals on zoom on September 16 at 10 am est.
you’ll receive the details to join in my newsletter email coming out to you soon 🦋
#yoga #aminatahamethod #app #iloveyou #practice
wearing @aloyoga

so grateful I get to be your mother.
